source.name: Geochemistry of Sediments in the US from the (NURE-HSSR) Database
source.description: Geochemical analyses of sediment samples throughout the U.S. collected by the hydrogeochemical and stream sediment reconnaissance (HSSR) phase of the National Uranium Resource Evaluation (NURE) program. This database contains 397,625 records.
